WEBVTT

01:40.560 --> 01:45.940
[Speed and Love]

01:46.210 --> 01:48.710
[Episode 21]

01:50.240 --> 01:51.680
Did you see the Luminous Pearl

01:51.680 --> 01:52.810
that night?

01:58.759 --> 01:59.570
Yes, I did.

02:01.290 --> 02:01.960
So

02:02.450 --> 02:03.570
when the explosion happened,

02:03.570 --> 02:04.450
you didn't...

02:29.800 --> 02:30.760
I'm not a god.

02:35.130 --> 02:36.930
I'm just an ordinary person too.

02:38.690 --> 02:39.760
What do you mean?

02:41.200 --> 02:42.030
You saved me.

02:47.480 --> 02:48.520
Were you hurt?

02:49.010 --> 02:49.850
Let me see.

02:52.079 --> 02:52.850
I'm fine.

03:04.850 --> 03:05.910
How is your mother?

03:12.130 --> 03:14.590
Chris has arranged
a second surgery for her.

03:14.800 --> 03:16.170
It went fairly well,

03:16.600 --> 03:17.890
but I'll have to go

03:18.090 --> 03:20.150
and see her in person to know for sure.

03:26.800 --> 03:28.130
You should go back soon.

03:30.970 --> 03:32.320
When people are sick,

03:34.079 --> 03:36.140
they need their family by their side.

03:42.980 --> 03:43.870
I'm sorry.

03:46.920 --> 03:48.360
I even asked you before

03:48.970 --> 03:51.170
if you wanted to go to Nanjing together.

03:51.570 --> 03:54.370
I never thought I'd be the one
who couldn't make it.

03:57.920 --> 04:00.120
We'll have plenty of time in the future.

04:01.450 --> 04:02.780
But your mom can't wait.

04:03.760 --> 04:05.320
After major surgery,

04:06.450 --> 04:08.730
a patient's mood is
the most important thing.

04:08.730 --> 04:09.970
If you stay with her,

04:10.360 --> 04:11.490
she'll feel better.

04:12.570 --> 04:14.100
It's good for her recovery.

04:20.839 --> 04:21.570
Are you...

04:26.040 --> 04:28.040
breaking up with me?

04:47.900 --> 04:51.010
♪ I leave after your curtain call ♪

04:50.010 --> 04:50.640
Come here.

04:53.610 --> 04:56.810
♪ I ask the tired bird ♪

04:57.600 --> 05:00.650
♪ About your news ♪

05:02.920 --> 05:06.570
♪ You're too serious in
both your passion and silence ♪

05:08.880 --> 05:14.070
♪ That's why you're always
covered in scars ♪

05:15.710 --> 05:19.320
♪ If darkness can stop the pain ♪

05:19.450 --> 05:24.640
♪ I'll let you sleep a bit longer ♪

05:26.180 --> 05:30.190
♪ I'll stay by your side tonight ♪

05:33.000 --> 05:38.120
♪ I want to meet the dusk with you ♪

05:38.480 --> 05:42.360
♪ Then stay with me until dawn ♪

05:43.140 --> 05:49.180
♪ Our moment together
feels like a lifetime ♪

05:49.280 --> 05:51.250
You should go out
and see more of the world.

05:49.630 --> 05:53.280
♪ Your remaining warmth before dawn ♪

05:53.520 --> 05:54.930
Maybe you'll find

05:53.760 --> 05:57.870
♪ Is enough for me to sink in soberly ♪

05:56.130 --> 05:58.200
there are many men out there
better than me.

05:58.200 --> 06:02.160
♪ But I'm still waiting
for every dawn and dusk ♪

06:02.180 --> 06:06.120
♪ To run towards you again ♪

06:07.210 --> 06:10.490
Even if I have only you in my arms

06:10.780 --> 06:15.010
♪ Meet the dusk with you ♪

06:15.500 --> 06:19.270
♪ Then stay with me until dawn ♪

06:19.910 --> 06:25.180
♪ Our moment together
feels like a lifetime ♪

06:26.620 --> 06:30.270
♪ Your remaining warmth before dawn ♪

06:30.380 --> 06:34.770
♪ Is enough for me to sink in soberly ♪

06:34.830 --> 06:36.830
♪ But I'm still waiting ♪

06:37.200 --> 06:38.850
♪ For every dawn and dusk ♪

06:38.870 --> 06:42.800
♪ To run towards you again ♪

06:43.180 --> 06:46.850
♪ Until I can embrace you ♪

06:49.060 --> 06:52.350
♪ For a lifetime ♪

07:01.320 --> 07:02.160
You're awake.

07:02.570 --> 07:03.770
Officer Lu just left.

07:03.840 --> 07:05.100
He left when I arrived.

07:05.720 --> 07:06.490
My phone.

07:35.370 --> 07:37.080
I'm planning to leave Manshi.

07:37.640 --> 07:40.240
Maybe I'll go somewhere far away
to try my luck.

07:40.520 --> 07:43.490
I won't be using this phone number
and this WeChat account anymore.

07:43.490 --> 07:45.550
Once I've settled down in a new place,

07:45.760 --> 07:47.090
I'll contact you again.

08:06.400 --> 08:07.050
Sanlai.

08:10.410 --> 08:11.460
Tomorrow...

08:14.440 --> 08:16.170
help me cancel my phone number.

08:18.490 --> 08:19.280
Brandy,

08:19.860 --> 08:21.660
isn't this too cruel to Jiang Mu?

08:25.420 --> 08:26.380
Cancel it.

09:14.760 --> 09:15.800
Happy birthday,

09:16.320 --> 09:17.110
Zhao.

09:43.680 --> 09:45.940
Mu's presence lingers everywhere here.

09:47.040 --> 09:48.040
Her laughter

09:49.040 --> 09:50.700
still seems to ring in my ears.

09:53.010 --> 09:55.140
But I have to say goodbye to all of this.

09:56.640 --> 09:57.370
I...

10:01.160 --> 10:02.820
I can't become a burden to her.

10:04.990 --> 10:06.590
As long as she's happy,

10:07.400 --> 10:08.800
that's all that matters.

10:31.250 --> 10:33.580
You've really decided to go back to China?

10:36.490 --> 10:38.090
I'll go back to school first,

10:38.610 --> 10:40.610
then see what I can build from there.

10:42.680 --> 10:44.730
Can you really bear to
leave the garage behind?

10:44.730 --> 10:45.780
I said back then,

10:45.800 --> 10:47.610
once the matter with Wan's was settled,

10:47.610 --> 10:48.610
I'd close it down.

10:51.010 --> 10:51.760
I know.

10:52.280 --> 10:55.880
By that time, you were already planning to
take Jiang Mu with you.

10:59.560 --> 11:00.560
Once you leave,

11:01.370 --> 11:03.430
our brotherhood will really be over.

11:06.330 --> 11:07.260
It won't be over.

11:08.640 --> 11:09.890
You two will come visit me
in China, won't you?

11:09.890 --> 11:10.490
Alright.

11:11.010 --> 11:12.290
Make something of yourself.

11:12.290 --> 11:13.690
When you're successful,

11:13.820 --> 11:15.220
we'll come leech off you.

11:16.850 --> 11:17.850
It's a deal, then.

11:33.040 --> 11:34.180
Pick up the pace.

11:34.200 --> 11:35.440
Mu will be here soon.

11:36.010 --> 11:36.810
Don't rush me,

11:36.850 --> 11:38.330
or I'll cut my hand.

11:40.330 --> 11:42.450
You have a comeback for everything I say.

11:42.450 --> 11:43.510
Hurry up and think.

11:44.440 --> 11:45.570
When Mu comes later,

11:46.800 --> 11:48.090
if she asks about Zhao,

11:48.090 --> 11:49.440
what should we tell her?

11:52.490 --> 11:54.280
Just say Jin Zhao went away
to look for better opportunities

11:54.280 --> 11:55.370
and never came back.

11:55.370 --> 11:56.730
Fine, fine, say it like that!

11:56.730 --> 11:58.090
What if she asks about

11:58.210 --> 11:59.680
his address or phone number?

11:59.680 --> 12:00.280
What then?

12:00.490 --> 12:01.560
Just say we don't have them either,

12:01.560 --> 12:03.360
and that he hasn't contacted us.

12:04.040 --> 12:05.370
Do you even have a brain?

12:05.440 --> 12:06.970
That obviously won't work.

12:07.010 --> 12:07.250
Mom.

12:07.250 --> 12:08.330
You think she'd buy that...

12:08.330 --> 12:09.900
I bought Mu's favorite

12:09.920 --> 12:10.920
strawberry milkshake.

12:10.920 --> 12:11.560
Good.

12:13.010 --> 12:13.730
Xin,

12:14.280 --> 12:16.010
when Mu comes,

12:16.680 --> 12:18.090
be careful what you say.

12:18.370 --> 12:20.280
If she asks about Zhao,

12:20.490 --> 12:21.210
just say,

12:21.970 --> 12:22.770
"I don't know.

12:22.970 --> 12:24.160
I don't know anything."

12:24.160 --> 12:24.680
Okay?

12:24.970 --> 12:26.520
That's lying.

12:28.010 --> 12:29.760
You're just a child. What do you know?

12:29.760 --> 12:30.680
Take this over there.

12:30.680 --> 12:31.740
I know everything.

12:31.920 --> 12:34.130
You and Dad are just being cruel.

12:38.000 --> 12:40.260
Did you hear that? Even our child says so.

12:42.490 --> 12:43.730
Tell me—are we being

12:43.780 --> 12:44.740
cruel here?

12:46.370 --> 12:48.490
Isn't it all for their own good?

12:53.610 --> 12:56.070
Mrs. Zhao, did Jin Zhao
ever come back later?

13:01.090 --> 13:01.920
No.

13:04.490 --> 13:06.250
Before heading out to make his own way,

13:06.250 --> 13:07.780
he came back home for a meal.

13:09.800 --> 13:11.660
At that time, he told your dad that

13:12.330 --> 13:13.130
if

13:13.680 --> 13:15.960
he managed to settle down over there,

13:17.050 --> 13:18.810
he might never come back.

13:19.520 --> 13:20.450
"Settled down?"

13:21.590 --> 13:22.630
What do you mean?

13:23.210 --> 13:24.870
Is he abandoning this family?

13:27.410 --> 13:28.200
Well...

13:33.570 --> 13:34.400
Mu,

13:35.440 --> 13:38.240
he's not your father's
biological son, after all.

13:39.210 --> 13:41.540
All these years he's lived alone outside,

13:41.900 --> 13:44.230
precisely because he didn't want us to...

13:44.880 --> 13:47.210
didn't want us to
worry too much about him.

13:47.730 --> 13:48.400
So,

13:48.680 --> 13:51.740
whatever ideas he has,
or whatever decisions he makes,

13:52.800 --> 13:53.590
we...

13:54.330 --> 13:56.330
have no position to influence him.

14:11.040 --> 14:12.540
Mrs. Zhao, I'm going out for a while.

14:12.540 --> 14:14.140
Don't wait for me for dinner.

14:48.490 --> 14:49.250
Sanlai,

14:49.760 --> 14:51.160
you closed your pet shop?

14:51.850 --> 14:52.640
Jiang Mu,

14:53.520 --> 14:55.320
weren't you studying in Canada?

14:55.760 --> 14:57.220
You're back in Manshi now?

15:00.580 --> 15:02.510
Do you have any news about Jin Zhao?

15:03.520 --> 15:04.520
Brandy?

15:05.060 --> 15:07.400
I haven't been in contact with him
for a long time either.

15:07.400 --> 15:09.730
That rascal.
Who knows where he ran off to?

15:09.920 --> 15:11.650
Not even a word to his own buddy!

15:11.860 --> 15:13.580
Stop looking for him. That rascal.

15:13.580 --> 15:15.310
Just forget about him already.

15:15.470 --> 15:16.660
Aren't there many

15:16.680 --> 15:18.490
handsome blonde, blue-eyed guys in Canada?

15:18.490 --> 15:20.010
You should get to know some.

15:20.010 --> 15:23.010
They're definitely better than
that rascal, Brandy.

16:55.930 --> 17:02.830
[Three years later]

17:08.770 --> 17:10.300
You live in Beijing, right?

17:10.369 --> 17:11.510
Yeah, I live in Beijing.

17:11.510 --> 17:12.660
It's cold there.

17:13.160 --> 17:13.730
Come on.

17:14.849 --> 17:15.640
Come on, welcome.

17:15.640 --> 17:16.430
Thank you very much.

17:16.430 --> 17:17.369
-Merry Christmas.
-Here comes the fish!

17:17.369 --> 17:18.530
Merry Christmas.

17:18.720 --> 17:19.329
Cheers.

17:23.119 --> 17:23.880
Mu.

17:24.810 --> 17:25.869
This is wonderful.

17:26.200 --> 17:28.200
Thank you so much for all of this, Mu.

17:28.290 --> 17:30.490
This Christmas feels especially nice.

17:31.090 --> 17:32.490
Thank you for joining us,

17:32.670 --> 17:34.330
and I'm thankful that your mom

17:34.530 --> 17:35.660
has recovered well.

17:36.530 --> 17:37.530
I'll go get her.

17:37.920 --> 17:39.090
Eat more later,

17:39.370 --> 17:39.930
okay?

17:40.290 --> 17:41.130
Come on, Nick.

17:41.230 --> 17:42.130
Keep her company, will you?

17:42.130 --> 17:42.680
Okay.

17:44.200 --> 17:46.600
Mu, did you make
all these dishes yourself?

17:46.690 --> 17:48.500
Did you cook often before?

17:50.130 --> 17:52.440
Would you believe me if I said

17:52.750 --> 17:55.680
I'd never cooked a complete meal
before coming here?

17:57.920 --> 17:59.650
This is incredibly delicious.

18:00.200 --> 18:01.090
People,

18:01.920 --> 18:03.480
they never stay the same.

18:21.630 --> 18:24.560
You should get her number.

18:27.540 --> 18:29.340
Hey, I would like to say, like...

18:29.870 --> 18:30.350
Sorry.

18:30.480 --> 18:31.810
I'd like... I want to...

18:32.560 --> 18:34.360
Can I have your number or some...

18:35.560 --> 18:37.080
Bro, no.

18:38.200 --> 18:38.800
Bro.

18:52.160 --> 18:52.920
Mu,

18:53.290 --> 18:54.330
I ground this coffee myself.

18:54.330 --> 18:55.790
Would you like to try some?

18:58.480 --> 18:59.480
No, thanks.

18:59.640 --> 19:00.610
Why do you never drink

19:00.610 --> 19:02.010
the coffee I make for you?

19:02.400 --> 19:03.640
I'm just afraid that
if I drink too much coffee,

19:03.640 --> 19:05.440
I won't be able to sleep at night.

19:06.890 --> 19:08.890
I'm meeting a few friends later.

19:09.050 --> 19:10.310
Would you like to join?

19:11.530 --> 19:12.160
Alright.

19:12.890 --> 19:14.530
Actually, there aren't any friends.

19:14.530 --> 19:15.400
It's just me.

19:17.160 --> 19:18.570
Why do you reject me

19:18.600 --> 19:19.930
every time I ask you out?

19:20.130 --> 19:21.720
Can't you give me a chance?

19:23.750 --> 19:25.720
Nick, I've noticed your Chinese

19:25.720 --> 19:27.050
has gotten really good.

19:27.250 --> 19:28.290
But I'm sorry,

19:28.440 --> 19:30.050
I have to turn you down again.

19:32.290 --> 19:33.960
Mu, you're so heartless.

19:35.640 --> 19:36.240
Fine then,

19:36.480 --> 19:37.680
I'll drink it myself.

19:48.480 --> 19:50.810
You know that, uh,
Character A in the game?

19:50.920 --> 19:53.370
My proficiency is through the roof.

19:53.890 --> 19:54.750
Do you want a go?

19:54.960 --> 19:57.490
I can give you a hand
and show you how it's done.

19:57.960 --> 19:58.800
And you know what?

19:58.800 --> 20:02.720
Now they've got so many competitions
with a lot of prize money as well.

20:02.810 --> 20:05.130
So, you never know. I could be rich.

20:05.160 --> 20:08.890
At the riverbank,
I caught the biggest fish, really.

20:08.920 --> 20:10.400
I was around there every morning,

20:10.400 --> 20:13.240
from six to four to six, all clock.

20:13.530 --> 20:15.200
From four to six, I am...

20:15.230 --> 20:17.860
I was waiting and waiting.

20:18.650 --> 20:19.610
I'm telling you,

20:19.640 --> 20:21.050
that basketball game the other day

20:21.050 --> 20:22.510
almost gave me a heart attack.

20:22.510 --> 20:24.430
First, we were up by so many points,

20:24.430 --> 20:28.960
but then, towards the middle of the game,
ultimately, I chucked a three-pointer.

20:30.160 --> 20:32.960
Causing us to win!
Putting a victory for our team!

20:34.130 --> 20:35.860
Have a sip of coffee if you want.

20:50.400 --> 20:51.680
Is this coffee good?

21:06.730 --> 21:09.460
It's probably not as good as
the one I make, right?

21:20.410 --> 21:21.810
The taste of my coffee...

21:24.050 --> 21:25.450
Do you still remember it?

21:42.480 --> 21:43.590
Why is it sweet?

21:47.480 --> 21:49.410
I won't let you have bitter things.

21:54.890 --> 21:55.720
I remember.

22:07.040 --> 22:10.410
By the way, I've got a basketball game
tomorrow. Do you want to come?

22:10.410 --> 22:11.170
Sorry.

22:12.390 --> 22:13.350
I'm tired.

22:23.410 --> 22:25.740
You should go out
and see more of the world.

22:26.640 --> 22:28.090
Maybe you'll find

22:29.250 --> 22:31.650
there are many men out there
better than me.

22:31.680 --> 22:32.530
See?

22:33.160 --> 22:34.610
I'm already 26 years old.

22:35.770 --> 22:36.970
After all these years

22:37.530 --> 22:38.850
of drifting and crossing paths

22:38.850 --> 22:40.180
with countless people,

22:41.050 --> 22:42.530
I still can't forget you.

22:48.860 --> 22:50.460
By the way, I'm from Nanjing.

22:50.660 --> 22:51.280
I did my undergraduate studies

22:51.280 --> 22:52.450
at Nanjing University
of Aeronautics and Astronautics.

22:52.450 --> 22:53.360
NUAA?

22:56.370 --> 22:58.720
I once wanted to study at NUAA too.

22:59.270 --> 23:00.640
But somehow, one thing led to another,

23:00.640 --> 23:01.970
and I ended up in Canada.

23:02.090 --> 23:02.850
Really?

23:03.160 --> 23:04.570
We have quite a connection then.

23:04.570 --> 23:05.960
We're even in the same field
for graduate studies.

23:05.960 --> 23:08.160
We should talk more about our research.

23:47.610 --> 23:48.290
Hey there.

23:49.000 --> 23:50.030
You're so dedicated.

23:50.030 --> 23:51.360
The pride of our nation.

23:52.200 --> 23:52.960
Thank you.

23:57.800 --> 23:58.950
May I take a look?

24:18.850 --> 24:20.200
Are you into fountain pens?

24:20.200 --> 24:20.960
A little bit.

24:22.610 --> 24:23.740
A gift from a friend?

24:25.160 --> 24:26.420
From my ex-boyfriend.

24:28.680 --> 24:30.640
You must've dated for quite a while.

24:30.640 --> 24:31.330
A week.

24:31.490 --> 24:33.550
A week, and he gave you a pen like this?

24:36.090 --> 24:37.200
An 18K gold nib,

24:37.530 --> 24:38.640
and the barrel and cap

24:38.640 --> 24:40.240
are pure silver with engravings.

24:40.240 --> 24:41.570
This is quite a nice pen.

24:42.100 --> 24:43.960
Your ex must've been pretty rich.

24:52.940 --> 24:54.140
He didn't have money.

24:54.920 --> 24:56.920
He just gave me the best thing he had

24:58.060 --> 24:59.790
when he was at his lowest point.

25:07.160 --> 25:08.820
That house was quite magical.

25:08.880 --> 25:10.240
The appliances were always breaking down,

25:10.240 --> 25:12.290
one after another,

25:12.440 --> 25:14.200
as if they'd planned it together.

25:14.200 --> 25:17.260
Jin Zhao always had no choice
but to go back and fix them.

25:18.400 --> 25:19.960
Your dad is good at driving

25:20.440 --> 25:21.810
but not much else.

25:22.190 --> 25:23.090
Being with him

25:23.240 --> 25:24.160
is exhausting.

25:24.480 --> 25:27.340
That's not true.
His cooking is actually very good.

25:27.720 --> 25:30.090
At least better than Jin Zhao's cooking.

25:32.360 --> 25:34.340
Jin Zhao can cook too?

25:35.380 --> 25:36.070
Yes.

25:36.530 --> 25:37.660
Not only can he cook,

25:37.770 --> 25:40.160
but he can also box, drive,

25:40.400 --> 25:41.240
and fix cars.

25:42.480 --> 25:43.990
And repair home appliances too.

25:43.990 --> 25:44.640
Yes,

25:44.930 --> 25:46.590
he can do just about anything.

25:52.720 --> 25:54.810
Although he was constantly framed
by Wan's,

25:54.810 --> 25:56.370
he never gave up

25:56.530 --> 25:57.990
or felt sorry for himself.

25:58.370 --> 25:59.290
In my opinion,

25:59.440 --> 26:01.900
he's a person
with a strong sense of justice.

26:04.060 --> 26:05.540
What is he doing now?

26:11.400 --> 26:12.160
I don't know.

26:12.680 --> 26:14.880
We haven't been in touch for a long time.

26:22.370 --> 26:24.480
The weather is so cool today.

26:25.010 --> 26:27.140
So after school, do you have any plans?

26:27.400 --> 26:30.050
Maybe we can take a walk.

26:30.200 --> 26:30.770
Fine.

26:31.260 --> 26:32.260
That sounds good.

26:32.720 --> 26:33.400
Jiang Mu.

26:35.040 --> 26:36.370
What are you doing here?

26:41.000 --> 26:41.680
Thank you.

26:41.920 --> 26:42.850
You're welcome.

26:45.130 --> 26:46.370
I'm here for work,

26:46.570 --> 26:49.030
on assignment for a collaborative project.

26:49.130 --> 26:50.190
After graduation,

26:50.290 --> 26:51.890
you really did go to Nanjing.

26:52.000 --> 26:54.570
Now you're at a branch of
the Chinese Academy of Sciences?

26:54.570 --> 26:55.610
I've been to many places,

26:55.610 --> 26:56.540
but I still think

26:56.850 --> 26:58.250
our hometown is the best.

26:59.480 --> 27:01.480
I spend most of my time
at the Purple Mountain Observatory now.

27:01.480 --> 27:04.130
That's where the asteroid "China"
was discovered.

27:04.130 --> 27:07.790
They've achieved outstanding
research results in recent years.

27:08.050 --> 27:09.200
That's great.

27:09.920 --> 27:11.050
I'm really envious.

27:11.330 --> 27:12.640
I haven't had a chance

27:12.640 --> 27:15.000
to visit the old observatory site
on the mountain to see the gnomon,

27:15.000 --> 27:17.290
armillary sphere, and other ancient
astronomical instruments.

27:17.290 --> 27:18.490
When do you graduate?

27:18.810 --> 27:20.410
Soon, just a few more months.

27:21.400 --> 27:22.370
I happen to have

27:22.370 --> 27:23.770
a research assistant position open.

27:23.770 --> 27:24.900
Are you interested?

27:24.920 --> 27:26.180
I could save it for you.

27:28.200 --> 27:29.200
I...

27:30.000 --> 27:30.640
No rush.

27:30.780 --> 27:32.960
You still have several months
until graduation.

27:32.960 --> 27:34.420
Think about it carefully.

27:37.850 --> 27:38.450
By the way,

27:38.770 --> 27:40.810
there's a small gathering here tomorrow.

27:40.810 --> 27:42.870
It's with colleagues who came with me

27:42.940 --> 27:44.420
and some local peers.

27:44.920 --> 27:45.720
Why don't

27:46.090 --> 27:46.820
you come too?

27:47.720 --> 27:48.930
I can introduce you around.

27:48.930 --> 27:49.540
Okay.

28:12.000 --> 28:13.680
Sorry, everyone, I'm late.

28:13.770 --> 28:14.400
Jiang Mu.

28:14.730 --> 28:16.810
Zhijie, aren't you going to introduce us?

28:16.810 --> 28:17.920
Allow me to introduce you all.

28:17.920 --> 28:19.450
This is my junior, Jiang Mu.

28:19.530 --> 28:20.370
Nice to meet you.

28:20.370 --> 28:21.300
Nice to meet you.

28:22.200 --> 28:23.370
This is my supervisor,

28:23.370 --> 28:23.890
Professor Gan.

28:23.890 --> 28:24.810
Nice to meet you, Professor.

28:24.810 --> 28:27.240
And these two are my colleagues
from the CAS.

28:27.240 --> 28:30.100
Those over there are my classmates
from Melbourne.

28:30.290 --> 28:31.150
Come on, have a seat.

28:31.150 --> 28:31.720
Hurry.

28:32.810 --> 28:33.480
Sit here.

28:36.160 --> 28:37.090
Come on, cheers.

28:42.290 --> 28:44.270
Mu, welcome to this gathering.

28:44.290 --> 28:45.550
Thank you, Professor.

28:48.330 --> 28:50.130
What's your field of study?

28:50.400 --> 28:51.800
I'm studying astronomy.

28:52.590 --> 28:54.990
Not many girls
study this field these days.

28:56.680 --> 28:57.480
That is...

28:57.770 --> 28:59.900
an exquisite die with a red bean heart?

29:01.240 --> 29:02.570
The agate within the jade die is

29:02.570 --> 29:04.960
carved into the shape
of red beans—love beans.

29:04.960 --> 29:07.730
This kind of hollow carving
with a red bean

29:07.920 --> 29:08.890
inserted inside

29:09.290 --> 29:10.530
makes all six sides appear red—

29:10.530 --> 29:13.290
that's what we call
"an exquisite die with a red bean heart."

29:13.290 --> 29:15.880
A symbol of deep longing.

29:16.160 --> 29:18.250
In ancient times, it was a token of love.

29:18.250 --> 29:19.850
It was popular for a while back then.

29:19.850 --> 29:21.290
Rarely seen nowadays.

29:21.610 --> 29:22.410
Very special.

29:23.850 --> 29:25.110
You're giving it to me?

29:26.330 --> 29:28.260
Now you're willing to give it to me?

29:28.530 --> 29:30.700
Before, no matter how I asked,
you wouldn't give it to me.

29:30.700 --> 29:31.700
So stingy.

29:33.090 --> 29:35.290
I really couldn't give it to you before.

29:36.120 --> 29:36.880
But now...

29:37.140 --> 29:38.750
Now why can you?

29:42.750 --> 29:45.350
I'd have to start
with the origin of this thing.

29:46.240 --> 29:48.640
I'll tell you about it slowly
in the future.

30:02.290 --> 30:04.330
I've tried to see the world.

30:05.200 --> 30:06.130
All these years,

30:06.770 --> 30:08.640
I've met many excellent people.

30:09.570 --> 30:10.810
But no one

30:11.420 --> 30:13.180
can make me feel anything.

30:14.440 --> 30:15.290
Because

30:16.330 --> 30:18.000
none of them is you.

30:31.570 --> 30:32.200
Mom,

30:32.640 --> 30:34.770
I want to go back to China for my career.

30:37.640 --> 30:38.570
Back to Nanjing.

30:46.440 --> 30:47.130
Senior!

30:48.560 --> 30:49.190
Jiang Mu.

30:50.200 --> 30:50.850
What is it?

30:51.090 --> 30:53.440
You mentioned yesterday
that you need a research assistant.

30:53.440 --> 30:54.240
Is that true?

30:54.680 --> 30:55.810
Of course it's true.

30:57.110 --> 30:58.640
You've decided so quickly?

30:58.960 --> 30:59.680
Yes.

30:59.810 --> 31:01.660
I'll go back as soon as I graduate.

31:01.660 --> 31:02.850
Didn't you say your family was here

31:02.850 --> 31:04.000
and you weren't planning to go back?

31:04.000 --> 31:04.860
I am going back.

31:05.160 --> 31:06.810
I also want to contribute to
our country's aerospace program,

31:06.810 --> 31:08.270
even if it's just a little.

31:09.000 --> 31:09.570
Alright.

31:09.630 --> 31:11.690
I'll contact them for you right away.

31:19.490 --> 31:20.330
Dad.

31:20.920 --> 31:22.050
Dad, Dad.

31:22.770 --> 31:24.850
Look, I've finished my homework.

31:25.370 --> 31:26.160
You promised

31:26.370 --> 31:27.770
to take me to the concert.

31:28.240 --> 31:29.610
Did I ever promise you that?

31:29.610 --> 31:30.570
Yes, you did.

31:30.660 --> 31:32.290
You can't break your promise.

31:32.290 --> 31:33.490
Why don't I remember?

31:34.200 --> 31:36.130
Your dad said he would,
so he won't break his promise.

31:36.130 --> 31:37.930
Come on, sit down. Food's ready.

31:37.960 --> 31:38.720
Mom,

31:39.130 --> 31:40.280
you have to back me up.

31:40.280 --> 31:41.410
I know. Now sit down.

31:44.370 --> 31:45.330
Mu, come on.

31:45.610 --> 31:46.640
Try my cooking

31:46.850 --> 31:48.250
and see if I've improved.

31:53.200 --> 31:54.460
Has there been any news

31:54.580 --> 31:55.620
from Jin Zhao?

31:59.960 --> 32:01.130
He sends money back,

32:01.890 --> 32:03.820
but he himself has never come back.

32:04.000 --> 32:05.770
We haven't heard much from him
in a long time.

32:05.770 --> 32:06.480
Yes,

32:06.890 --> 32:08.950
he hasn't come back for so many years.

32:09.000 --> 32:09.960
Who knows,

32:10.370 --> 32:13.100
maybe he's already
settled down somewhere else.

32:15.050 --> 32:15.810
Right?

32:19.000 --> 32:19.630
Eat up.

32:20.240 --> 32:21.100
Have some more.

32:34.620 --> 32:35.480
Have some more.

32:35.810 --> 32:36.610
Thank you.

32:40.090 --> 32:41.850
Seriously, how long did it take you
to pass the exam?

32:41.850 --> 32:43.970
I got in the second year after you left.

32:43.970 --> 32:44.920
I've already graduated

32:44.920 --> 32:46.370
and returned home
to take over the family business.

32:46.370 --> 32:48.680
I'm working as a purchasing manager
at my dad's factory.

32:48.680 --> 32:50.540
I'm doing pretty well for myself.

32:51.160 --> 32:52.120
I can see that.

32:52.850 --> 32:53.710
What about you?

32:53.960 --> 32:55.360
How have you been lately?

32:57.330 --> 32:58.130
Oh, right!

32:58.570 --> 33:00.160
I always thought

33:00.160 --> 33:02.000
you and Brandy were related.

33:02.200 --> 33:03.330
I kept quiet about it for years

33:03.330 --> 33:05.050
and never dared to say anything.

33:05.050 --> 33:07.330
It wasn't until last year,
when Brandy came back, that I realized

33:07.330 --> 33:09.640
you two aren't actually related by blood.

33:09.640 --> 33:10.680
He came back?

33:11.370 --> 33:12.330
When?

33:12.610 --> 33:14.240
Early last year.

33:14.440 --> 33:17.130
There was a problem with a shipment
at my dad's factory.

33:17.130 --> 33:18.960
I couldn't find a replacement anywhere.

33:18.960 --> 33:20.760
Then I got a call from a stranger.

33:20.770 --> 33:21.920
He said he had the goods

33:21.920 --> 33:23.720
and quoted me a price

33:23.960 --> 33:26.850
lower than the market average.

33:27.100 --> 33:28.160
I thought it was a scam,

33:28.160 --> 33:30.090
so I insisted on meeting in person.

33:30.240 --> 33:31.200
To my surprise,

33:31.440 --> 33:32.640
it was Brandy!

33:38.620 --> 33:39.790
How is he doing?

33:40.370 --> 33:41.770
I'm not really sure

33:41.770 --> 33:43.370
how he's doing now.

33:43.850 --> 33:46.160
I offered to take him out for a meal

33:46.160 --> 33:47.290
to properly thank him that day.

33:47.290 --> 33:48.800
But he said he was short on time

33:48.800 --> 33:49.680
and that he could only stay for one day.

33:49.680 --> 33:51.840
He helped us connect with new suppliers

33:51.840 --> 33:53.040
and left the next day.

33:54.000 --> 33:54.600
Oh, right.

33:54.720 --> 33:56.890
I remember he brought someone
with him that day,

33:56.890 --> 33:57.780
called him "Boss,"

33:57.780 --> 33:59.780
and was very respectful toward him.

34:05.730 --> 34:06.810
Then... how was

34:07.570 --> 34:08.850
his health?

34:10.770 --> 34:11.730
He looked worn out.

34:11.730 --> 34:13.810
Probably tired from traveling.

34:14.040 --> 34:15.730
But he was still as handsome as ever.

34:15.730 --> 34:17.460
He hasn't lost his charm at all.

34:21.090 --> 34:22.630
It was precisely because of the time

34:22.630 --> 34:24.650
when Brandy helped me turn things around

34:24.650 --> 34:25.909
that I was finally able

34:25.920 --> 34:27.770
to establish my authority
at my dad's factory

34:27.770 --> 34:29.040
and gain some real influence.

34:29.040 --> 34:31.300
No one called me a nepotism hire anymore.

34:32.440 --> 34:33.960
Later, I found out

34:34.290 --> 34:36.400
why Brandy suddenly contacted me.

34:38.400 --> 34:39.250
Why?

34:40.730 --> 34:41.940
Do you remember

34:41.980 --> 34:43.670
when you brought Brandy

34:43.690 --> 34:45.600
to my dad's factory to fix the car?

34:47.250 --> 34:49.230
At that time, Brandy told me

34:49.250 --> 34:50.580
he owed me a favor

34:50.600 --> 34:52.080
and would repay it someday.

34:52.080 --> 34:54.210
I thought he was just being polite.

34:54.210 --> 34:55.920
I had completely forgotten about it.

34:55.920 --> 34:58.960
I never expected him to remember
after all these years!

34:58.960 --> 35:01.560
I really respect him
for being a man of his word!

35:03.700 --> 35:04.370
Cheers.

35:07.220 --> 35:09.820
He even remembered the favor
he owed to Pan Kai,

35:10.080 --> 35:11.960
so why did he promise to contact me

35:12.250 --> 35:13.710
but never follow through?

35:18.080 --> 35:19.330
Do you have his contact information?

35:19.330 --> 35:20.520
Could you share it with me?

35:20.520 --> 35:21.520
You don't have it?

35:24.890 --> 35:27.020
I'll send it to you. I'll send it to you.

35:29.260 --> 35:30.320
I've sent it to you.

35:31.890 --> 35:33.440
He came back last year.

35:33.920 --> 35:34.980
His family is here,

35:35.040 --> 35:37.440
so there's no reason
he wouldn't go see Dad.

35:37.850 --> 35:39.480
He's not a heartless person.

35:40.120 --> 35:41.400
Back when things were so difficult,

35:41.400 --> 35:43.560
he even risked breaking the law to
modify cars to help pay for Xin's surgery

35:43.560 --> 35:44.890
and support the family.

35:44.940 --> 35:46.000
There's no way
he would just disappear forever

35:46.000 --> 35:47.400
after the case was over.

35:48.330 --> 35:49.890
But why would Dad say

35:50.440 --> 35:52.520
he hasn't come home for several years?

35:52.520 --> 35:53.810
It's also possible

35:54.440 --> 35:55.640
that he did come back,

35:56.040 --> 35:57.480
but for some reason,

35:57.650 --> 35:59.250
Dad chose to hide it from me.

35:59.560 --> 36:01.760
But what reason could Dad possibly have

36:01.770 --> 36:03.080
for doing that?

36:10.690 --> 36:12.890
Dad, I'm already on the plane.

36:13.130 --> 36:14.810
Take care of yourself and Mrs. Zhao.

36:14.810 --> 36:16.040
When Xin's on holiday,

36:16.040 --> 36:17.480
bring her to Nanjing for a visit.

36:17.480 --> 36:18.040
Okay.

36:18.440 --> 36:19.570
Have a safe journey.

36:19.770 --> 36:21.170
Let me know when you land.

36:25.640 --> 36:27.040
She's boarded the plane.

36:32.330 --> 36:33.190
Do you think...

36:34.470 --> 36:36.640
she's found out we lied to her?

36:40.600 --> 36:41.560
Probably not.

36:43.120 --> 36:45.180
Did she ask you about Zhao in private?

36:53.030 --> 36:55.070
Mu is such a good girl.

36:55.730 --> 36:57.860
Is it okay for us to lie to her like that?

36:58.200 --> 36:59.860
This was Jin Zhao's decision.

37:05.250 --> 37:06.360
I feel so uneasy...

37:11.210 --> 37:12.940
But this is all we can do for now.

37:51.400 --> 37:53.210
Brother, I want strawberries!

38:47.920 --> 38:48.690
Zhao.

38:49.710 --> 38:50.750
I'm back.

38:52.170 --> 38:53.250
Do you remember?

38:54.120 --> 38:56.210
This is where we grew up together.

38:57.520 --> 38:58.960
I told you before—

38:59.520 --> 39:00.690
when I was little,

39:01.170 --> 39:02.440
I'd secretly come back to our old house

39:02.440 --> 39:04.370
and leave my contact information,

39:04.810 --> 39:06.400
hoping that one day, when you returned,

39:06.400 --> 39:07.480
you could find me.

39:08.250 --> 39:09.770
At that time, I had a hope

39:10.730 --> 39:12.330
that as long as you came back,

39:12.600 --> 39:14.380
maybe you'd use the same method

39:14.400 --> 39:15.860
to leave me some messages.

39:16.770 --> 39:19.210
So I could find you too.

39:20.520 --> 39:21.360
But...

39:22.310 --> 39:23.420
Zhao, look.

39:24.060 --> 39:25.720
Everything here has changed.

39:26.580 --> 39:29.380
Changed so much
I don't even recognize it anymore.

39:30.560 --> 39:31.360
Zhao,

39:32.440 --> 39:33.950
can I still find you?

39:35.400 --> 39:36.600
Where are you really?

39:38.210 --> 39:40.870
Are we really going to
miss each other like this?

39:41.650 --> 39:42.850
Should I really...

39:44.080 --> 39:45.190
let you go?
